summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6764, for the improvement of 60th Avenue Southwest, from West Charleston Street to Wet Spokane Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 43604 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
